# Session [22] – Network+

## Main Topics
- VLAN chist?  
- Tarze kar VLAN  
- Estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – VLAN Basics
- VLAN = Virtual LAN  
- VLAN **device ha ra az LAN fiziki joda mikonad** baraye segmentation  
- Hame device dar LAN mitavanand be VLAN haye mokhtalef vasl shavand  

## Explanation

### Tarze Kar
- Switch VLAN aware → port ha ro assign mikonad be VLAN specific  
- Traffic VLAN joda mishavad → broadcast domain joda  
- Routers/VLAN trunk baraye ersal traffic be VLAN digar  

### Estefadeh-ha
- Security behtar → devices VLAN digar nemitavanand directly access konand  
- Bandwidth optimize → broadcast ha limited mishavad  
- Network management easier  

### Example Table
| Port | VLAN ID | Device |
|------|---------|--------|
| 1    | 10      | PC-A   |
| 2    | 10      | PC-B   |
| 3    | 20      | PC-C   |
| 4    | 20      | AP     |

